  "detailed_description": "<h1>Feature List</h1><p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>6 different characters you can play with<br></li><li> 8 Interface Languages<br></li><li> 6 different Alphabets (ABC)<br></li><li> 3 difficulties suitable for all ages (Easy 7-12, Normal 9-15, Hard 15+)<br></li><li> Intra-word usage and pronunciation for each letter</li></ul></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong>Language Learning Simulator - Alphabet</strong>  is an educational game that allows players to learn new alphabets easily and in a fun way!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Find the letters in the forest, and carry them to the Wall of Wisdom<br></li><li>Be careful! There are wild animals on the road!<br></li><li>Use Safety Stops or tree trunks to protect yourself from wild animals. Animals do not like to climb on them.<br></li><li>Have fun!</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Language Learning Simulator - Alphabet</strong>  is an educational game that allows players to learn new alphabets easily and in a fun way!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Find the letters in the forest, and carry them to the Wall of Wisdom<br></li><li>Be careful! There are wild animals on the road!<br></li><li>Use Safety Stops or tree trunks to protect yourself from wild animals. Animals do not like to climb on them.<br></li><li>Have fun!</li></ul>",
